quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,166,"Wareede barminee foolee ko heﾉ砥noo on kon ﾃｱalnde uhud tuma nde fedde mon nden fottunoo e fedde sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko e Duﾅ蟻yee Alla e Koddoruyee Makko ; hikma fii no O gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n feeﾃｱira."
  3,167,"E fii no naafiqi en feeﾃｱira, ﾉ兎n wi'ananooﾉ兎 : "Haﾉ妬ree fii laawol diina Alla ngol, maa duﾃｱiron ﾉ兎 sabu ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁ngol juulﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n", ﾉ兎 wi'i: "Hara nun meﾉ容n anndunoo ko fii hare men jokkayno on, si ko woni, men anndaali fii nde hare hakkunde mon e maﾉ橡兎". Kamﾉ兎 non nden ﾃｱalnde, hari ko keeferaaku ngun ﾉ砥runoo ﾉ殿ﾉ葉aade ﾉ兎 e dii gomﾉ擁nal ngal : hiﾉ兎 wowlira kunndule maﾉ橡兎 kon ko alaa e ﾉ兎rnde maﾉ橡兎. Ko Alla ﾆ「ri Anndude kon ko ﾉ兎 wirnii e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎, O Leptirayﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m."
  3,168,"Ko ﾉ兎 salii yahugol ka hare, ﾉ兎 wi'ani ﾉ殿ﾉ熔ndiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 barmunooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n uhud: "Hara nun ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftino men ﾉ兎 roﾅ橘i yahude ka hare, ﾉ兎 waretanooke". Maakanﾉ兎 an Annabiijo: "Duﾃｱee pottinon ndee maayde e pittaali mo'on si nde arii e mo'on tawi kadi ko on goognuﾉ兎 e ko aaﾆｴotoﾉ熔n wonnde si ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftino on ﾉ兎 waretanooke, e wiide kadi on daﾉ擁raali maayde nden si wanaa salagol mon yahude ka jihaadi fii laawol diina Alla ngol."
  3,169,"Wata a sikku an Annabiijo, wonnde ﾉ兎n waraaﾉ兎 ka jihaadi fii laawol diina Alla ngol ko maayuﾉ兎, ko woni, ko wuuruﾉ兎 nguurndam heeriiﾉ預m ka Joomi maﾉ橡兎, hiﾉ兎 e galle teddungal, hiﾉ兎 arsikee noone kala e neemaaji ﾉ擁 tawata ko Alla tan Anndi ﾉ擁."
  3,170,"Hiﾉ兎 huuﾉ妬ri weltaare ko Alla Neeminiri ﾉ兎 e ﾆ「ral Makko, hiﾉ兎 jortii nde musiﾉ遼兎 maﾉ橡兎 heddiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka aduna tawta ﾉ兎 ; wonnde si ﾉ兎n waraama ka jihaadi, ﾉ兎 daﾃｱay ﾉ砥ral sifa maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 wonaa hulooﾉ兎 fiyaake laakara, ﾉ兎 wonaa kadi sunoytooﾉ兎 e kon ko faatiiﾉ兎 e geﾉ登y aduna."
  3,171,"Hiﾉ兎 weltora ndii mbarjaari mawndi ndi ﾉ兎 habbori Alla, e ﾉ兎ydaneede ndin mbarjaari mawndi. E wonnde pellet, Alla bonnataa njoﾉ電i gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Mo ﾉ兎n, si ko woni, O Hunnanay ﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i maﾉ橡兎 ndin no timmiri, O ﾆ‘ydana ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m."
  3,172,"ﾆ‘n nootiiﾉ兎 noddaandu Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on tuma nde ﾉ兎 noddanoo yahugol ka hare fii laawol diina Alla, ﾉ兎 hawroya e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka hare "hamraa' al Asad" hikkiinde nden uhud, ﾉ殿awo nde ﾉ兎 barmunoo ﾃｱalnde uhud ; ﾉ兎 saloraaki noddaandu Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on sabu barme maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n. Hino woodani ﾉ兎n moﾆｴﾆｴimﾉ兎 e maﾉ橡兎 golle, ﾉ兎 huli Alla ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftii Yamrooje Makko ﾉ容n ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁tii Haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n ; njoﾉ電i mawndi immorde ka Alla, ndi woni Aljanna."
  3,173,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 yoga e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'annoo: "Pellet Qurayshi en e ﾉ熔wro Abuu Sufyaana mooﾉ登ndiranii on e ﾉ蓉uﾉ預l fii haﾉ砥gol on mula fii mon, reﾅ逆ee e maﾉ橡兎 hulon ﾉ兎". Kan haala hulineede ﾉ兎ydaali ﾉ兎 si wanaa goongingol Alla hooloo fodoore Makko nden, ﾉ兎 yalti haﾉ登ygol hiﾉ兎 wi'a: "Alla Toowuﾉ熔 On yonii men, O yonii yonndinorteeﾉ熔"."